2026-05-15T05:06:01.3463612Z 12    <!--
2026-05-15T05:06:01.3463999Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T05:06:01.3464351Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T05:06:01.3465060Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T05:06:01.3465606Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T05:06:01.3466044Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
